content: First, Andriod tablets are made with different specifications/hardware so meaning your tablet/phone might not function well. I am using a 10inch Samsung 4th gen tablet and the touchscreen sensors arent as good as I would like it to be. Sometimes when trying to press 2 or 3 buttons the latency is delayed. but its my tablet not the apps fault. Overall its a good tool when combined with my real Hohner Panther to practice finger techniques. oh its ad free
